{"tid":1994004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[又係IT] Uber首席科技官請辭 據報研裁員兩成料涉逾5,400人","createTime":"2020-04-29T07:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T13:07:11.000Z","uid":38316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1fb5ef98c0079138c44b00f47e2bb85be1a1b2","tid":1994004,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"據美國網約車巨擘優步(Uber)向美國證交會(SEC)遞交文件指，首席科技官Thuan Pham請辭，將於5月中旬離任。<br />\n<br />\n另據外媒報道，由於新冠疫情下出行大幅減少，Uber正研究裁員兩成，現階段尚未確實，倘成事，意味公司2.7萬名員工中，將有逾5,400人「飯碗不保」，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括約800個工程職位</span>。(da/k)"},{"pid":"8f58fbce48d5f0ce366ef8fb25a38fb8ecfd451f","tid":1994004,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"IT狗未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa388034a54adb6f72799c64d820e7dd1a6c9cb","tid":1994004,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb424edcc5048e99bf2ead8988093f6f6a1afceb","tid":1994004,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"仲想做it既入來講兩句"},{"pid":"c66f885a8ec0a946ed89cdf755a6e560908fd23d","tid":1994004,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb424edcc5048e99bf2ead8988093f6f6a1afceb","tid":1994004,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"仲想做it既入來講兩句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"IT 一向都係最慘"}]}